@startuml agentic_vs_antigravity_flow
!theme plain
skinparam actorStyle awesome

' Global dark theme settings
skinparam backgroundColor #000000
skinparam defaultFontColor #FFFFFF

' Note specific settings
skinparam note {
    BackgroundColor #FFFFFF
    BorderColor #000000
    FontColor #000000
}

' Sequence styling
skinparam sequence {
    LifeLineBorderColor #FFFFFF
    LifeLineBackgroundColor #000000
    ParticipantBorderColor #FFFFFF
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #000000
    ParticipantFontColor #FFFFFF
    GroupBackgroundColor #000000
    GroupBodyBackgroundColor #000000
    GroupBorderColor #FFFFFF
    GroupFontColor #FFFFFF
    DividerBackgroundColor #000000
    DividerBorderColor #FFFFFF
    DividerFontColor #FFFFFF
    ArrowColor #FFFFFF
    BoxBorderColor #FFFFFF
    BoxBackgroundColor #111111
    BoxFontColor #FFFFFF
}

' Colors
!$USER_COLOR = "#FFB6C1"
!$MANAGER_COLOR = "#90EE90"
!$A1_COLOR = "#87CEEB"
!$A2_COLOR = "#DDA0DD"

title Google Antigravity Flow — "Create Instagram API package"

actor "USER\n(IDE)" as U $USER_COLOR
participant "MANAGER\nVIEW" as M $MANAGER_COLOR
participant "AGENT 1\n(workspace)" as A1 $A1_COLOR
participant "AGENT 2\n(workspace)" as A2 $A2_COLOR

autonumber

== Spawn Agents ==

U -[$USER_COLOR]> M: "create Instagram"
activate M $MANAGER_COLOR

M -[$MANAGER_COLOR]> A1: spawn agent 1
note right: cloud startup
activate A1 $A1_COLOR
M -[$MANAGER_COLOR]> A2: spawn agent 2
activate A2 $A2_COLOR

== Parallel Work (each with growing context) ==

A1 -> A1: Write entities\n+ ALL tools per call\ncontext grows\n~60K tokens
A2 -> A2: Write handlers\n+ ALL tools per call\ncontext grows\n~60K tokens

== Artifact Production ==

A1 -[$A1_COLOR]> M: produce Artifact\n(screenshot, plan)
M -[$MANAGER_COLOR]> U: Artifact 1
A2 -[$A2_COLOR]> M: produce Artifact
M -[$MANAGER_COLOR]> U: Artifact 2
deactivate A2

== Feedback Loop ==

U -[$USER_COLOR]> M: feedback on Artifact
M -[$MANAGER_COLOR]> A1: resume agent 1

A1 -> A1: more Write calls
A1 -> A1: Bash: build + test
A1 -> A1: Bash: git push
deactivate A1

M -[$MANAGER_COLOR]> U: final Artifact

deactivate M

note over U
  **TOTAL: ~115,000 tokens**
  **COST: ~$1.10-$1.40**
  **TIME: 10-20 minutes**
  No typed entities
  No capability manifest
  No deterministic code gen
  Agents are independent
  Artifacts are visual, not machine-readable
  Knowledge base saves context for future
end note

@enduml
